OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cool, unsettled day with some
OL,6,Fsunny spells and frequent showers.
OL,7,FHeaviest showers, with hail and
OL,8,Fisolated thunderstorms, develop across
OL,9,Fcentral and southern UK during the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Breezy conditions continue,
OL,11,Fwith coastal gales later in the far
OL,12,Fnortheast.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers become confined to
OL,15,Fnorthern-facing coasts, with long dry
OL,16,Fperiods and some clear spells inland.
OL,17,FTurning chilly overnight with local
OL,18,Frural frost. Windy in the far
OL,19,Fnortheast with coastal gales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
