OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA cold start with patchy frost
OL,6,Fin prone areas. Largely dry with
OL,7,Fvariable cloud, a few light showers
OL,8,Fmainly eastern coasts. Breezy early in
OL,9,Feast, easing, temperatures slightly
OL,10,Fbelow average.
